	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Yeah, a bank register addressed at each 4k page would be fine.<br /><br />Yeah, if the high bank is initialized at powerup that should be enough. I'm sure I could manage a stub in every bank that's mapped there. The problem I was concerned about was having to put a stub in all the banks.<br /><br />There's probably no need to map anything to $6000. It might be a convenient place for some player code, but since $8000-BFFF is available to swap some code in anyway, it's not necessary.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
